data.description: Come See this 3 Sided Brick 5BR/3.5 BA w/ Large Bonus Room Located Inside The Highly Sought After Durham Lakes Golf & Country Club Community. Built in 2019, This Home Features an Open Floor Plan With High Vaulted and Tray Ceilings, Tons of Natural Light, Separate Dining Room that Easily Seats 10, Formal Living Room and Eat in Kitchen w/ Island Overlooking a Large Family Room w/ Brick Fireplace. Other Features Include Stainless Steel Appliances, Oversized Master on Main w/ Seating Area w/ Covered Back Patio Entrance, Walk-In-Closet and Soaking Tub. Upstairs, Four Spacious Bedrooms are Connected by two Jack and Jill Bathrooms w/ a Large Bonus Room. Located Only Minutes From I-85, Hartsfield Jackson International Airport & Trilith. Durham Lakes Has Wonderful Amenities Including an Active HOA, Swimming Pool, Clubhouse, Tennis Courts, Playground & Golf Course! Come Make This Beautiful Home Your Own. Schedule Your Tour Today!
